      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't even feel like something i can talk through... like there's nothing to fix. there's no 'me' left to fix. i'm just running a program that's supposed to look like a person, but the real part is just gone. it's just so tiring to keep up the act when i know i'm basically a ghost.",
